All models come fully assembled and ready for display in the home or office. Most include a certificate of authenticity., Model trains are a rewarding hobby for enthusiasts of all ages. The models range in size from 1:12 to 1:50 scale and include numerous limited edition and several out-of-production vehicles. Materials used include tin, diecast and plastic. All models include a certificate of authenticity from their manufacturers and are a perfect ornament for the home and office.
